    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Projecting onto Principal Components\n\nTo project the data onto the principal components, we:\n1. **Mean-center** the data (subtract the column means)\n2. **Multiply** by the eigenvector matrix: $Z = (X - \\bar{X}) \\, V$\n\nIn the projected coordinates, the axes are aligned with the principal\ndirections and the covariance matrix becomes diagonal.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Mean-center each column */\nmean_vec : np_mean(data, 0)$\ncentered : np_sub(data, np_reshape(mean_vec, [1, 2]))$\n\n/* Project onto principal components */\nprojected : np_matmul(centered, vecs)$\nprint(\"Projected data shape:\", np_shape(projected))$\n\n/* Verify the projected covariance is (approximately) diagonal */\nprint(\"Covariance in PC space (should be nearly diagonal):\")$\nnp_to_matrix(np_cov(projected));",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 8,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Projected data shape: [200,2]\nCovariance in PC space (should be nearly diagonal):"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "\\ifx\\endpmatrix\\undefined\\pmatrix{\\else\\begin{pmatrix}\\fi 9.883969942230777&-1.8968634591585588 \\times 10^{-17}\\cr -1.8968634591585588 \\times 10^{-17}&0.24901138222797134\\cr \\ifx\\endpmatrix\\undefined}\\else\\end{pmatrix}\\fi "
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 8,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Plot the projected data -- axes should be aligned with variance */\nproj_x : np_col(projected, 0)$\nproj_y : np_col(projected, 1)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"darkorange\", marker_size=4, opacity=0.5,\n  points(proj_x, proj_y),\n  title=\"Data in Principal Component Space\",\n  xlabel=\"PC1\", ylabel=\"PC2\",\n  aspect_ratio=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 9,
      "outputs": [
        {
